ğŸŠ **SETUP COMPLETE!** 

Your Claude ParadoxChat system is fully operational with:
âœ… Claude-3 Sonnet integration
âœ… Advanced logical consistency checking  
âœ… Automatic response refinement
âœ… Comprehensive analysis dashboard
âœ… Export capabilities

Start asking Claude complex questions and watch the logical analysis in action! ğŸ§ ğŸŒ€
""")
